author: stsp
msg: Fix issue #4161 "Assertion failed with svn diff -r BASE:HEAD ^/trunk"
This change prevents the assertion and causes an error message instead:
"svn: E195002: PREV, BASE, or COMMITTED revision keywords are invalid for URL"
(check_paths): Do not claim that a URL with a local revision was a local path.
